SWN On May 21 2019 at the Companys annual meeting of shareholders the Annual Meeting the Companys shareholders voted to approve an amendment to the Southwestern Energy Company 2013 Incentive Plan as previously amended the 2013 Plan to increase the number of shares of the Companys common stock that the Company is authorized to issue or award under the 2013 Plan by 36000000 shares to a total of 88700000 shares the Incentive Plan Amendment The Incentive Plan Amendment was adopted by the Companys Board of Directors effective as of May 21 2019 subject to shareholder approval
